Class AddAPartControllerScreen

java.lang.Object
nwalters.inventorytrackingsystemproject.AddAPartControllerScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AddAPartControllerScreen extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class launches the ADDAPartForm.fxml. This class allows the user to add a part with the appropriate data. This data then will get transfered to the main menu screen.
